---
title: Sweet Apple Pork Chops with Cauliflower Mash and Snap Peas
description: Pork has a way of embracing fruity flavors like no other protein. In this recipe, we’re smothering it in chunks of tender, saucy apple, which add a welcome touch of sweetness to the mild flavor of the meat. On the side, we’ve got sugar snap peas and a mash that tucks cauliflower into the potatoes—it’s so good, your kids won’t notice you snuck in some extra veggies!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-with-cauliflower-mash-w04-1b19f348.jpg
